{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 This example shows how to print memo fields that vary in size.\par
\par
To do this, you need to set two properties:\par
\par
1. The memo field control needs to have the \cf2 Multi-line edit\cf1  property set to \i\f1 Yes\i0\f0 .\par
\par
2. The Form property \cf2 Expand Form\cf1  needs to be set to \i\f1 One Page\i0\f0  or \i\f1 Multi-Page\i0\f0 .\par
}
